\f1 \cf2 {\listtext	\'95	}Includes 5% on perceived effiiciency (as validated in the code), and 5% on the quality of the algorithm for suggesting a change to branch X given a change in branch Y.
\f0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720
